      "content_text": "SHBA i heq \u201cnon grat\u00ebn\u201d Berish\u00ebs/ Bo\u00e7i: Dit\u00eb krenarie p\u00ebr PD. Ju mundi t\u00eb gjith\u00ebve \n\nPas 5 vitesh, Departamenti Amerikan i Shtetit (DASH) i ka hequr \u201cnon grat\u00ebn\u201d kryedemokratit Sali Berisha.\n\nDeputeti i PD, Lu\u00e7iano Bo\u00e7i gjat\u00eb fjal\u00ebs s\u00eb tij n\u00eb Kuvend tha se kjo \u00ebsht\u00eb nj\u00eb dit\u00eb krenarie p\u00ebr PD dhe se t\u00eb gjitha mashtrimet dhe shpifjet kund\u00ebr kryedemokratit ran\u00eb posht\u00eb. \n\nLEXO M\u00cb SHUM\u00cb N\u00cb TVKLAN.AL\n\n#TvKlan #Lajme  #Lu\u00e7ianoBo\u00e7i",
